  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of olive oil in a skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the diced bell pepper and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Add the minced thyme, chopped cilantro, garlic powder, and salt. Stir to combine.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and stir in the shredded cheese until melted and well combined.",
    "Add the sliced jalapeño and stir to combine.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a lacquerware bowl and drizzle with remaining 1 tablespoon of olive oil and 2 tablespoons of lime juice.",
    "Garnish with additional cilantro if desired."
  ],
